"""
        Type annotations should be included in the set of
        """
spec = ArgSpec(args=('a', 'b'), varargs=None, varkw=None, defaults=None,
    kwonlyargs=(), kwonlydefaults=None, annotations=(('a', int), ('b', str)))
self.assertEqual(_getArgNames(spec), {'a', 'b', ('a', int), ('b', str)})
